@startuml
title ArcHub CMS - Domain Events Flow
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

component "Application service" as App
component "ArcHubDomainEvent" as Event
component "Audit handler" as Audit
component "Webhook handler" as Webhook
component "Cache invalidation handler" as Cache
component "Runtime export handler" as Runtime
component "Search/index handler" as Search
database "Activity log" as Activity
queue "Webhook deliveries" as Queue
folder "Runtime snapshots" as Files

App --> Event : return explicit events
Event ..> Audit : future adapter
Event ..> Webhook : future adapter
Event ..> Cache : future adapter
Event ..> Runtime : future adapter
Event ..> Search : future adapter
Audit --> Activity
Webhook --> Queue
Runtime --> Files
@enduml
